description: This skill offers the ability quickly get information about elements on the periodic table. You can ask for an element by either name or symbol, and the Chemistry Professor will know what you're looking for. So if you can't remember which element Na is or what the symbol for potassium is, just ask the Chemistry Professor for a reminder.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Chemistry Professor what Na is
Alexa, ask Chemistry Professor what the symbol is for potassium
Alexa, ask Chemistry Professor to tell me about carbon
name: Chemistry Professor
shortDescription: Quickly get information about elements on the periodic table. Can't remember which element Na is? Just ask the Chemistry Professor.
